* ''The Americans''. McDougal Littell, Evanston, 1998. (Multiple later and variant editions) {{ISBN|0395851823}}
* ''World History: An Atlas and Study Guide''. Prentice Hall, 1998. {{ISBN|0130953822}}

===2000s===
